const Icon = () => {
  return (
    <svg
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
  width="192"
  height="192"
  fill="#000000"
  viewBox="0 0 256 256"
>
  <rect width="256" height="256" fill="none"></rect>
  <polyline
    points="216 72 104 184 48 128"
    fill="none"
    stroke="#000000"
    stroke-linecap="round"
    stroke-linejoin="round"
    stroke-width="16"
  ></polyline>
</svg>
  )
};

export default Icon;
